docs {
  # Get Decision Statistics
  
  Get aggregated decision statistics.
  
  ## Response
  - `totalDecisions`: Total number of decisions
  - `allowedDecisions`: Number of allowed decisions
  - `deniedDecisions`: Number of denied decisions
}
